text: 189th may refer to: *189th (Canadien-Français) Battalion, CEF, a unit in the Canadian Expeditionary Force during the First World War *189th Airlift Squadron, a unit of the Idaho Air National Guard that flies the C-130 Hercules *189th Airlift Wing, an airlift unit located at Little Rock AFB, Arkansas *189th Infantry Brigade (United States) ==See also== *189 (number) *189, the year 123 (CLXXXIX) of the Julian calendar
